features: Wide Compatibility Type-C Hardwire Kit：The 13ft dash cam hardwire kit only support devices with Type-C ports, please check and confirm your device first. Type C Hardwire Kit can directly connect the almost all dash cam in the markets to the car/truck/suvs/bus for continuous power.
Hardwire Kit for 24 Hours Parking Surveillance：Connect the on-board power supply for an uninterrupted power supply,support 24/7 recording,providing protection for your car.

Hardwire Kit for Dash Camera with Low Voltage Protection：With low voltage protection function, the dash cam will auto shut down when input voltage drops to under 11.6v(23.6V for 24V input) Leaving enough power to ensure that the car can start normally.

Easy to Use：The usb c dash cam hardwire kit is equipped with clips and crowbars, help you open the car insurance box and install more convenient. No need for cable from car cigarette lighter socket,hidden wiring simple and keeps the car neat and tidy.

Tips：Please read the quick guide carefully before use.If you have any questions about dashcam hardwire kit,please feel free to contact us. Accessory Cord/Battery Cord（Red）-- Connect to the fuse whose power will be always on regardless of whether the engine is on or off. Ground Cord（Black）-- Connect to metal part of the fuse box（Negative pole of power supply，usually attached to the screw）

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great dash cam hardwire kit
reviews.reviewText: Includes all accessories you may need to hardwire dash cam, and works with newer USB-C dash cameras. Zero problems with installation or usage. Highly recommended. Great value compared to name brand kits that are the exact same thing

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No more cigarette lighter adapter
reviews.reviewText: Installed this wire kit on my dash cam this weekend. I was able to run use the cigarette lighter fuse as the power source. Plenty of line to get to the fuse box. No more cigarette lighter adapter to power up my dash cam. So much better and cleaner. I definitely recommend this if you have a dash cam that is powered up by USBC. Or you can always get an adapter.
